title: Standing female figure
description:
Standing Female Figure, ceramic, West Mexican (Chupicuaro), 250BC - 300AD NO PHOTO ON CAT. CARD cat. card dims H 5\'.
Solid, unslipped clay with red and white pigments. Applique headband, earplugs and necklace. Right arm missing.
creditline: Gift of Lucille and Arthur Weiss
